s.detail:
Thunder Turret: DC 20 to find, DC 15 to disable;
    initiative +3, 1 attack per round, affects all targets within a 20 ft. cone, DC 15 save or take 18d10 thunder damage
    and become deafened for 1d4 rounds

south.trap:
Thunderstone Mine: DC 15 to find, DC 20 to disable;
    affects all targets within 20 ft., DC 13 save or take 18d10 thunder damage
    and become deafened for 1d4 rounds

trap:
Poisoned Net Trap: DC 10 to find, DC 15 to disable;
    affects all targets within a 10 ft. square area, DC 19 save or take 24d10 poison damage
    and become restrained, half damage on a successful save
